[
  {
    "startTime": 1.99,
    "endTime": 4.573,
    "text": "(upbeat music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.582,
    "endTime": 11.100000000000001,
    "text": "- Hello everyone and welcome back"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.1,
    "endTime": 12.51,
    "text": "to English with Lucy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.51,
    "endTime": 14.49,
    "text": "Today, I'm going to talk to you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.49,
    "endTime": 18.34,
    "text": "about all the phrasal\r\nverbs that go with turn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.34,
    "endTime": 20.04,
    "text": "So this video is going to be excellent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.04,
    "endTime": 22.13,
    "text": "for improving your vocabulary,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.13,
    "endTime": 23.369999999999997,
    "text": "which, in turn, will help you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.37,
    "endTime": 25.3,
    "text": "with your listening and your speaking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.3,
    "endTime": 27.400000000000002,
    "text": "However, if you want\r\nto take your listening"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.4,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "and your pronunciation to the next level,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 33.32,
    "text": "I highly recommend\r\nlistening to audio books."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.32,
    "endTime": 35.46,
    "text": "And, in my opinion, the best platform"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.46,
    "endTime": 37.89,
    "text": "for downloading audio books is Audible."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.89,
    "endTime": 40.08,
    "text": "If you want to improve your pronunciation,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.08,
    "endTime": 42.07,
    "text": "choose a British narrator,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.07,
    "endTime": 45.27,
    "text": "for example, Stephen Fry\r\nreading Harry Potter,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.27,
    "endTime": 46.900000000000006,
    "text": "and read the physical book"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.9,
    "endTime": 49.05,
    "text": "as you're listening to the audio book."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.05,
    "endTime": 50.529999999999994,
    "text": "That is the perfect way"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.53,
    "endTime": 52.88,
    "text": "to improve your listening\r\nand your pronunciation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.88,
    "endTime": 55.080000000000005,
    "text": "I can offer you one free audio book,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.08,
    "endTime": 57.12,
    "text": "that's a 30 day free trial."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.12,
    "endTime": 58.739999999999995,
    "text": "All you've got to do is click on the link"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.74,
    "endTime": 60.64,
    "text": "in the description box and sign up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.64,
    "endTime": 64.29,
    "text": "Right, let's get on with\r\nthe phrasal verb lesson."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.29,
    "endTime": 66.58000000000001,
    "text": "So the first one, pretty easy,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.58,
    "endTime": 68.86,
    "text": "we have to turn on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.86,
    "endTime": 70.5,
    "text": "And this means to start a device"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.5,
    "endTime": 71.8,
    "text": "by switching it on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.8,
    "endTime": 73.03999999999999,
    "text": "That's a synonym."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.04,
    "endTime": 73.93,
    "text": "For example."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.93,
    "endTime": 75.05000000000001,
    "text": "Can you turn off the lights"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.05,
    "endTime": 76.56,
    "text": "when you leave please?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.56,
    "endTime": 78.84,
    "text": "Also note that to turn on a person"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.84,
    "endTime": 82.245,
    "text": "means to excite them emotionally."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.245,
    "endTime": 84.745,
    "text": "(romantic music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.745,
    "endTime": 85.846,
    "text": "And physically."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.846,
    "endTime": 87.67,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.67,
    "endTime": 89.32000000000001,
    "text": "But I'm sure if you are interested in that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.32,
    "endTime": 91.52999999999999,
    "text": "then you can google it yourself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.53,
    "endTime": 93.3,
    "text": "I'm not talking about it here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.3,
    "endTime": 96.36,
    "text": "Then we have number two, to turn off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.36,
    "endTime": 98.69,
    "text": "This means to stop a device"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.69,
    "endTime": 100.50999999999999,
    "text": "by switching it off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.51,
    "endTime": 101.35000000000001,
    "text": "For example."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.35,
    "endTime": 103.75999999999999,
    "text": "Turn off the TV and listen to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.76,
    "endTime": 106.66000000000001,
    "text": "And it can also mean to\r\nreally not excite somebody"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.66,
    "endTime": 108.66,
    "text": "emotionally or physically."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.66,
    "endTime": 112.00999999999999,
    "text": "Now, slightly more difficult, to turn out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.01,
    "endTime": 115.2,
    "text": "To turn out means to result or to end up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.2,
    "endTime": 116.47,
    "text": "For example."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.47,
    "endTime": 118.23,
    "text": "Oh, I thought my homework"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.23,
    "endTime": 120.65,
    "text": "was gonna turn out better than this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.65,
    "endTime": 122.04,
    "text": "I thought my homework was going"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.04,
    "endTime": 124.05000000000001,
    "text": "to end up better than this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.05,
    "endTime": 125.35,
    "text": "Number four."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.35,
    "endTime": 127.70299999999999,
    "text": "Pretty simple, to turn around."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.72,
    "endTime": 132.0,
    "text": "I almost fell over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.0,
    "endTime": 134.96,
    "text": "To turn around means to rotate,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.96,
    "endTime": 136.97,
    "text": "to physically rotate something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.97,
    "endTime": 137.92,
    "text": "For example."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.92,
    "endTime": 140.72,
    "text": "Turn around, you've left\r\nthe label in your jacket."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.72,
    "endTime": 143.58,
    "text": "A situation can also turn around."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.58,
    "endTime": 145.81,
    "text": "You can also turn back,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.81,
    "endTime": 147.04,
    "text": "and this is to return"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.04,
    "endTime": 148.92,
    "text": "to a previous state of being."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.92,
    "endTime": 149.86999999999998,
    "text": "For example."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.87,
    "endTime": 153.0,
    "text": "Once you move out,\r\nthere's no turning back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.0,
    "endTime": 155.48,
    "text": "You cannot return to living with me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.48,
    "endTime": 158.14,
    "text": "Once you move out, you can't turn back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.14,
    "endTime": 160.51999999999998,
    "text": "We also have to turn against,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.52,
    "endTime": 163.55,
    "text": "and to turn against means to oppose,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.55,
    "endTime": 164.70000000000002,
    "text": "often suddenly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.7,
    "endTime": 166.29,
    "text": "So someone who was your friend"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.29,
    "endTime": 169.25,
    "text": "might turn against you\r\nand become your enemy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.25,
    "endTime": 170.44,
    "text": "For example."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.44,
    "endTime": 172.85999999999999,
    "text": "We were great friends and\r\nthen she turned against me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.86,
    "endTime": 174.96,
    "text": "and started gossiping about me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.96,
    "endTime": 176.75,
    "text": "Then we have to turn in,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.75,
    "endTime": 179.19,
    "text": "and this means to submit something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.19,
    "endTime": 180.67,
    "text": "or to give something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.67,
    "endTime": 181.503,
    "text": "For example."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.503,
    "endTime": 183.27999999999997,
    "text": "I want you all to turn in your homework"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.28,
    "endTime": 184.86,
    "text": "on Monday morning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.86,
    "endTime": 186.9,
    "text": "Next, we have to turn down,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.9,
    "endTime": 188.83,
    "text": "and this means to refuse,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.83,
    "endTime": 191.13000000000002,
    "text": "decline or reject something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.13,
    "endTime": 192.74,
    "text": "For example."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.74,
    "endTime": 195.27,
    "text": "I asked him out but he turned me down,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.27,
    "endTime": 196.96,
    "text": "he rejected me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.96,
    "endTime": 199.21,
    "text": "We also have to turn into,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.21,
    "endTime": 202.12,
    "text": "and this means to\r\ntransform into something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.12,
    "endTime": 203.02,
    "text": "For example."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.02,
    "endTime": 204.56,
    "text": "She clicked her fingers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.56,
    "endTime": 207.1,
    "text": "and he turned into a frog."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.1,
    "endTime": 209.21,
    "text": "Finally, we have to turn up,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.21,
    "endTime": 211.20000000000002,
    "text": "and this means to appear suddenly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.2,
    "endTime": 213.13,
    "text": "or to attend an event."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.13,
    "endTime": 214.07999999999998,
    "text": "For example."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.08,
    "endTime": 216.54000000000002,
    "text": "Oh, look who just turned up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.54,
    "endTime": 219.4,
    "text": "And this means, Oh,\r\nlook who just appeared!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.4,
    "endTime": 222.43,
    "text": "Oh, look who is attending the event!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.43,
    "endTime": 224.45000000000002,
    "text": "Right, that's it for today's lesson."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.45,
    "endTime": 225.64999999999998,
    "text": "I hope you learned something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.65,
    "endTime": 226.88,
    "text": "and I hope you enjoyed it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.88,
    "endTime": 229.01,
    "text": "Please give me some recommendations"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.01,
