  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.6,
    "endTime": 231.59,
    "text": "that you would like to see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.59,
    "endTime": 234.34,
    "text": "I'd love to do lots of\r\nwork on phrasal verbs"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.34,
    "endTime": 237.15,
    "text": "as I'm noticing a lot of\r\nerrors in the comments."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.15,
    "endTime": 238.64000000000001,
    "text": "Your homework for today is to pick"
